sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as Student
  participant FE as Frontend RAG Panel
  participant APP as app.go
  participant RET as retrieval.Service
  participant GEN as generation.Provider

  U->>FE: Ask question
  FE->>APP: StreamRAGAnswer(question)
  APP-->>FE: event channel name
  FE->>APP: Subscribe via EventsOn(channel)

  Note over APP: Current state emits demo chunks
  APP-->>FE: chunk events
  APP-->>FE: done event with sources

  Note over APP,RET: Planned full wiring
  APP->>RET: Retrieve top chunks (HyDE + RRF)
  RET-->>APP: Context chunks
  APP->>GEN: GenerateStream(prompt, onToken)
  GEN-->>APP: token callbacks
  APP-->>FE: chunk events from model stream
  APP-->>FE: done with grounded sources